pre code strong {
    color: #ffd700;  /* Gold for emoji headers */
    font-size: 1.1em;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
}
```

**Why:** Modern gradient look (VS Code dark theme style), not boring gray boxes

