### Breathing Room

- ‚úÖ Add blank lines between sections
- ‚úÖ Use horizontal rules (`---`) to separate major sections
- ‚úÖ Don't cram content together
- ‚úÖ Use tables to naturally space content
- ‚úÖ Add margins in CSS styling

